OL,3,CFamily of man who fell to his death
OL,4,Cfrom Holborn balcony appeal for
OL,5,Cwitnesses
OL,7,FThe family of a man who fell to his
OL,8,Fdeath after the balcony of his flat in
OL,9,FHolborn gave way are appealing for
OL,10,Fwitnesses.
OL,12,FJoshua Robbins, 23, died after falling
OL,13,Fin his fifth storey flat at Holland
OL,14,Fand Thurston Dwellings on Newton
OL,15,FStreet on January 29 2026.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
