OL,3,CFamily of man who fell to his death
OL,4,Cfrom Holborn balcony appeal for
OL,5,Cwitnesses
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police are
OL,8,Finvestigating what happened and
OL,9,FJoshua's family are now asking anyone
OL,10,Fwho worked at, or was contracted to
OL,11,Fwork at, Thurstan Dwellings during the
OL,12,Fweeks leading up to his death to come
OL,13,Fforward.
OL,15,FThey would like to hear from anyone
OL,16,Fwho was involved in maintenance,
OL,17,Fpainting, decorating, inspection,
OL,18,Fsupervision or management, as well as
OL,19,Fresidents or contractors who may have
OL,20,Fhad concerns about the condition of
OL,21,Fthe railings.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
