OL,3,CFamily of man who fell to his death
OL,4,Cfrom Holborn balcony appeal for
OL,5,Cwitnesses
OL,7,FJoshua's mother, Fiona Garrett, said
OL,8,Fthey are "determined to establish the
OL,9,Ftruth".
OL,11,F"We understand that some people may
OL,12,Ffeel they have nothing important to
OL,13,Fadd, or may be anxious about speaking
OL,14,Fto the police.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1783684141
OL,3,CFamily of man who fell to his death
OL,4,Cfrom Holborn balcony appeal for
OL,5,Cwitnesses
OL,7,F"As Joshua's parents, we simply ask
OL,8,Fthat if you saw anything relating to
OL,9,Fthe condition of the railings, the
OL,10,Fmaintenance works, or any issues at
OL,11,FThurstan Dwellings, however
OL,12,Finsignificant it may seem, please come
OL,13,Fforward."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
